										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">On Friday, USDCAD will focus on job data from the US and Canadian economies.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;"> <img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-31890" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/USDCAD-–-Daily-Chart.png" alt="USDCAD – Daily Chart" width="790" height="598" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/USDCAD-–-Daily-Chart.png 790w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/USDCAD-–-Daily-Chart-300x227.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/USDCAD-–-Daily-Chart-768x581.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px" /></span></p>
